:

*Prelepo* je to što si me tako pohvalio. (It's beautiful that you praised me like that.)

*Prelepo* je učiniti nešto za druge. (It's wonderful to do something for others.)

*Prelepim* detaljima učinićeš svoj dom još lepšim. (You will make your home even more beautiful with beautiful details.)

*Prelepom* bojom obojićeš svoj život. (You will color your life with a beautiful color.)

*Prelepo* je to što je ona toliko pozitivna. (It's wonderful that she is so positive.)